uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean

Class DiffBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.tool.bean.DiffBean

  • public class DiffBean
extends Object
    DiffBean is a helper bean which given an RWikiObject and some strings representing the chosen left and right revision numbers will determine which revisions have been chosen and create a GenericDiffBean from the contents.
    Version:
    $Id: DiffBean.java 84222 2010-11-03 13:15:52Z david.horwitz@uct.ac.za $
    Author:
    andrew
    See Also:
